  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>All our cabins are either semi-detached or in a terraced row of 3 or 4 cabins. Cabin exteriors can be made from either round or planed logs.</p>
<p><strong>One bedroom cabins </strong>are around 45m² with a 10m² mezzanine. They can sleep 2 - 4 people, with one twin bedroom downstairs and two mattress beds on the mezzanine. These cabins have an open-plan living room/kitchenette. Cabins that sleep up to five people, with a third bed on the mezzanine are also available. </p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom cabins </strong>are about 57m² and can sleep 3 - 6 people. The cabins have two twin bedrooms. Groups of 5-6 people will be allocated a cabin with a mezzanine (about 20m²) with two extra beds. Groups of 1-4 people may be allocated a cabin without a mezzanine.</p>
<p><strong>Cabin facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Equipped kitchen (facilities include an oven, fridge, microwave, toaster, coffee-maker, dishwasher)</li>
<li>TV </li>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Fireplace (small supply of wood included)</li>
<li>Drying closet</li>
<li>Washing machine</li>
<li>One shower</li>
<li>One WC</li>
<li>One linen and towel set included, per person per week</li>
<li>Beds to be made up on arrival</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Cabin requests</strong></p>
<p>If you would like to request a specific cabin name it is possible to do so at the time of booking through the Inghams Reservations Team.</p>
<p>These are some of the cabins typically allocated to Inghams guests:</p>
<p><strong>One bedroom cabins (4 people)</strong> Ylläsröhkö, Musko, Peltola, Veerantupa, Veramukka, Lumipolku, Sapara</p>
<p><strong>One bedroom cabins (5 people):</strong><span> Teerentie, Sapara, Veramukka</span></p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom cabins:</strong> Hillankukka, Lumipolku, Sapara, Reporanka, Ylläsniesta, Teerentie</p>
<p>If you are a returning customer, exact cabin numbers may also be requested.</p>
<p>Your request will be shared with our cabin partner and nearer to your departure date we will contact you to advise if your request has been granted. It is not possible to guarantee a specific cabin name or provide availability overviews and this may mean we are contacting you to advise your request cannot be met. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
